# web-build

Minimal Emscripten build folder for Minecraft LCE web target.

- **src/** and **data/** are copied from web-fixed; do not edit here if you want changes to persist in web-fixed.
- Build script: `project/emscripten/build_web.ps1`. Uses emcc, expects emsdk at `../../../emsdk` (sibling of web-build).
- Run `install_deps.ps1` first to install/activate emsdk.
- Outputs: `index.html`, `index.js`, `index.wasm` in `project/emscripten/`.
